OOC: D'oh! I keep forgetting what Wheeljack did! Okay, scratch that post.

:::Wheeljack/Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian/Atma/Psuedo:::

Wheeljack: Why, yes it does.  I put those sheilds up myself.  Hmm, turrets 
under water sounds like an excellent idea.
~~~~~
::My Predacons wake up and go outside.  There they see Drillbit talking to 
Megaton. Starscream cannot beleive his eyes::
Starscream: YOU?
::He remembered their dogfight back in the arctic::
~~~~~
::Atma and Psuedo immeadiately see that Burning Hammer is the enemy::
Atma: Thats right, were here to help you.
::Atma takes out his gun and fires 25 shots at Burning Hammer.  Psuedo fires 
2 missles from each of his two guns at Burning Hammer::
